item.description:
Behind the Scenes of Book 4: From Dream to Reality Why a Book 4? It’s true, after all, wasn’t the story supposed to end at the conclusion of Book 3?
As a true Rouennais, I’ll answer “Maybe yes, maybe no!” The most attentive among you will have noticed that mysterious message at the end of Book 3, “Les Triades”:
&ldquo;Hello, Ace of Hearts? Ace of Clubs here. You’ll never believe what’s happening…&quot;
